<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_107" id="53r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"/>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_107_r2l21"><expan>Fritʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> hunt ein betbrief / von <expan>einſhalbe<ex>n</ex></expan> tüchs </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_107_r2l22">wegen von prüchſel / das er <expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan> pfincʒing </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_107_r2l23">beÿ Tumpach <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> hat / das Jm Nicklas </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_107_r2l24">vveiſʒ von vvönſidell füret <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> Jn <expan>vig<ex>i</ex>l<ex>i</ex>a</expan> <expan>Aſcenſio<ex>n</ex>is</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_107" id="53r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab/></div>
